Bots:

* [https://emacs.ch/@emacslife @emacslife@emacs.ch]
* [https://emacs.ch/@rssbot @rssbot@emacs.ch]

If you want to access Mastodon from Emacs, try [https://codeberg.org/martianh/mastodon.el mastodon.el].

Mastodon timelines are RSS-compatible: to follow a given user account via RSS, you only need to add '.rss' to their user handle, as in:

'https://symbolics.social/@slartibartfast.rss'

This means that to access Mastodon via Emacs, you can also use [[Elfeed]], [[GnusRss]], or any of the methods listed under [[Rss]].

